    "description": "Description:<br><br>Peasant Kingdom is a medieval PVP game where players can build castles, craft items, fight other players with a wide variety of historical weapons, besiege and defend castles.<br><br><strong>Ranged combat:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/6608dadb32f66c30409f3c1c916af29b.poster.avif?t=1692622413\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/6608dadb32f66c30409f3c1c916af29b.webm?t=1692622413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/6608dadb32f66c30409f3c1c916af29b.mp4?t=1692622413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take part in exciting battles with a wide variety of throwing weapons. Each of these weapons has its own unique characteristics and involves a specific playstyle.<br><br><br><strong>Melee combat:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/605571acf48a2dfccfa084001bfb5fde.poster.avif?t=1692622413\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/605571acf48a2dfccfa084001bfb5fde.webm?t=1692622413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/605571acf48a2dfccfa084001bfb5fde.mp4?t=1692622413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Melee combat is represented by full control over the direction of the weapon's strike and the position of the shield. To block an enemy strike, you need to cover exactly the area in which the strike is directed.<br><br><br><strong>Building:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/be33ff7b4ea061f6efd0888b592d622e.poster.avif?t=1692622413\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/be33ff7b4ea061f6efd0888b592d622e.webm?t=1692622413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/be33ff7b4ea061f6efd0888b592d622e.mp4?t=1692622413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Design your castles in such a way that it is more difficult for other players to besiege them. The possibilities of the game offer a lot of scope for various tricky castle designs.<br><br><br><strong>Placeables:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/c038df8cec977752860a13c8fd1f26f7.poster.avif?t=1692622413\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/c038df8cec977752860a13c8fd1f26f7.webm?t=1692622413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301750/extras/c038df8cec977752860a13c8fd1f26f7.mp4?t=1692622413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build structures that will help you craft items, cook food, process resources and much more.<br><br>Contact email: <a href=\"mailto:lucky18.inc@gmail.com\">lucky18.inc@gmail.com</a>",
